{
  "_comment": "Canonical field schema for buyer-file automation. 'fields' = unique canonical fields across all forms, grouped by scope. 'forms' = per-form mapping from canonical field to PDF field name(s), with optional transforms. Static brokerage values live in defaults.json (keyed by PDF field name). The filler combines defaults.json (always) + this schema's per-form mappings (per-deal data). Fields with a 'derived' block are computed from other canonical fields at fill time.",

